 index between perpetual and spot prices. The funding formula incorporates a base rate of 0.01% plus the premium component, with payments occurring at 00:00, 08:00, and 16:00 UTC. Portfolio margin mode allows traders to optimize capital efficiency by using cross-collateral positions to reduce margin requirements across multiple perpetual contracts."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
